						<summary>

						

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year: <hi rend="italic">Saumya, Āshāḍha śu.</hi> 5.</hi></p>						

						<p>In characters of the 16th century A.D. Records the grant of land with all its appurtenances to the gods Prasanna-Veṅkaṭēśvara and Mallikārjuna of Āvulapalle. Further it also records the excavation of tank in the village by Prekarāyagaru. Mentions one Suguṭṭuru Chikkarāya Timmayyagavuṇigaru.</p>						

						</summary>
